Move magazine is reporting that a family spokesperson for the Ncwane family has confirmed that Sfiso was admitted to hospital for kidney failure. It s believed that the gospel singer died in a Johannesburg hospital this morning.Drum magazine earlier reported that his sister Gugu confirmed his death but was too upset to elaborate on the details.A family spokesperson has confirmed that Sfiso was rushed to hospital after suffering from kidney complications reports Move. Sfiso passed on after an alleged kidney failure. He was rushed to the hospital last night after he allegedly complained about kidney problems said Sipho Makhabane.It has also been reported by Move that the Ku Lungile Baba hit maker was vomiting blood last night.